WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.634
<i>Previously on</i> Greenleaf...

00:02.636 --> 00:04.035
I just think
you should calm down

00:04.038 --> 00:05.704
on the groupies
at the cotillion.

00:05.705 --> 00:07.539
- Isaiah.
- Get off!

00:07.541 --> 00:11.577
I promise you I will
never do this again.

00:11.579 --> 00:13.112
<i>Excuse me, First Lady?</i>

00:13.114 --> 00:15.481
- Yes?
- I meant First Lady Skanks.

00:15.483 --> 00:17.416
When Kerissa and I
were doing Real Church,

00:17.418 --> 00:19.418
we met some amazing people,

00:19.420 --> 00:21.020
<i>and we need them here.</i>

00:21.022 --> 00:23.022
Creating new programs
at a time like this?

00:23.024 --> 00:25.424
It may be better to wait on
your Real Church integration.

00:25.426 --> 00:28.160
Tamela Mann asked me
to sing backup for her.

00:28.162 --> 00:30.295
I do not want to see you

00:30.297 --> 00:32.131
throw away your dignity.

00:32.133 --> 00:34.666
- Mama!
- The one good thing about your mother

00:34.668 --> 00:36.135
leaving us the way she did.

00:36.137 --> 00:38.070
She knew about you, too.
All of them.

00:38.072 --> 00:40.072
<i>I could have ended my marriage.</i>

00:40.074 --> 00:43.108
You are <i> disgusting.</i>

00:43.110 --> 00:45.344
Tell Mae I'm sorry.

00:48.182 --> 00:51.083
<i>EnchantÃ©, madame.</i>

00:52.219 --> 00:53.519
<i>Monsieur.</i>

00:55.000 --> 01:01.074
